div.div:
DiffWithFragmentId()
Find matching objects with the same ID stored in a Fragment of choice.
If no match is found,objects are "added" or "removed" depending if they are exclusive to the following/past list.
Matched objects are compared and their property difference is returned: you get "Modified" or "Unchanged" objects, and the "Modified properties" per each modified object.
